      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems like a lot of warnings for something that's literally just a plant. i've read online that most people use them together for mild cases without any issues. if i just take a very low dose of the st johns wort once in a while when i'm feeling particularly bad, it shouldn't really cause a \"syndrome\" or anything, right? it's just natural stuff vs a tiny bit of medicine.",
